Fitness Tracker (YOLOv8-based)
Copyright (c) 2025 luohui1

This project includes modified code from the following open-source projects:

1) Exercise-Counter-with-YOLOv8-on-NVIDIA-Jetson (Apache-2.0)
   https://github.com/yuyoujiang/Exercise-Counter-with-YOLOv8-on-NVIDIA-Jetson

Modifications made in this repository include (but are not limited to):
- GUI desktop application (Tkinter) with control/settings tabs
- Chinese text rendering via PIL, pause/continue/stop, keyboard shortcuts
- Threshold hysteresis, debouncing, side selection (avg/left/right)
- Fitness statistics dashboard, daily goals, streaks, calendar view
- Config/history persistence (config/thresholds.json, config/history.json)
- Setup scripts (setup.bat/setup.ps1) and system check (check_system.py)
- Performance optimizations (YOLOv8n-pose default, device/half/imgsz)

Third-party components remain licensed under their respective licenses.

